WEBVTT

00:01:26.840 --> 00:01:28.570
Since your first day at school,

00:01:28.640 --> 00:01:29.840
I've noticed you.

00:01:29.960 --> 00:01:31.680
Because in your eyes,

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:33.600
there's a fragile beauty

00:01:33.640 --> 00:01:34.840
that breaks my heart.

00:01:36.039 --> 00:01:37.120
But...

00:01:39.080 --> 00:01:41.080
it seems like something is missing.

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:43.120
Right.

00:01:43.759 --> 00:01:45.039
It lacks a kind of

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:47.440
feminine charm.

00:01:47.640 --> 00:01:48.080
Come.

00:01:49.080 --> 00:01:50.009
Don't be afraid.

00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:50.720
Come here.

00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:04.560
Let me help you.

00:02:07.640 --> 00:02:08.440
Trust me.

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:10.720
Only I can help you.

00:02:43.880 --> 00:02:45.880
Enforce the law strictly, serve the people.

00:02:45.880 --> 00:02:46.280
Captain Sun,

00:02:46.280 --> 00:02:46.880
I'm sorry.

00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:50.530
I couldn't bring Jia Peng back.

00:02:53.440 --> 00:02:55.500
Jia Peng doesn't like people crying.

00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:57.800
If you cry,

00:02:57.880 --> 00:02:58.940
he'll feel sad too.

00:03:04.440 --> 00:03:05.970
Pull yourselves together.

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:08.240
What he couldn't finish,

00:03:09.240 --> 00:03:10.500
we will finish for him.

00:03:14.800 --> 00:03:15.240
Go.

00:03:45.280 --> 00:03:45.920
Master.

00:03:50.320 --> 00:03:51.800
You're finally here.

00:03:52.040 --> 00:03:53.600
I already bought you the fried dough sticks.

00:03:53.600 --> 00:03:55.400
Mr. Han said he put it on your tab.

00:03:57.040 --> 00:03:57.920
Just kidding.

00:03:58.520 --> 00:03:59.640
You're out of tea.

00:03:59.640 --> 00:04:01.170
I'll go get you another pot.

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:03.660
Let me refill your tea.

00:04:50.600 --> 00:04:51.280
Master.

00:04:52.320 --> 00:04:53.880
You must be exhausted lately.

00:04:53.880 --> 00:04:54.320
Here.

00:04:54.440 --> 00:04:55.300
Wash your face.

00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:03.360
Master.

00:05:04.680 --> 00:05:05.410
I'm leaving.

00:05:57.480 --> 00:05:59.140
Liu Jiang only contacted you.

00:05:59.680 --> 00:06:00.840
Then how did the killer know

00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:02.500
he was in Lianshui at the time?

00:06:03.320 --> 00:06:04.520
I don't know either.

00:06:05.080 --> 00:06:06.440
I really only told you.

00:06:06.840 --> 00:06:08.240
I've been fully cooperating.

00:06:08.240 --> 00:06:09.570
Think carefully again.

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:11.850
This concerns your husband's safety.

00:06:12.080 --> 00:06:14.440
Is it possible you were careless somewhere

00:06:14.440 --> 00:06:15.080
and leaked

00:06:15.400 --> 00:06:16.400
the information?

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:17.920
I really didn't.

00:06:18.160 --> 00:06:19.120
About this kind of thing,

00:06:19.120 --> 00:06:20.720
how could I dare tell anyone?

00:06:23.040 --> 00:06:23.600
However,

00:06:24.920 --> 00:06:26.250
I lost my phone that day.

00:06:26.840 --> 00:06:27.480
Does that count

00:06:27.480 --> 00:06:28.540
as being careless?

00:06:28.840 --> 00:06:29.500
You lost it?

00:06:29.720 --> 00:06:30.280
Yes.

00:06:30.600 --> 00:06:31.280
But I already reported this

00:06:31.280 --> 00:06:32.680
to Officer Jia.

00:06:41.680 --> 00:06:43.080
For the social app on that phone,

00:06:43.080 --> 00:06:44.400
the last logged-in IP location

00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:45.360
was on Minzhu Road.

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:46.880
And the phone signal disappeared at

00:06:46.880 --> 00:06:48.960
the intersection of Datong Street and Jianguo Road.

00:06:48.960 --> 00:06:50.960
The SIM card must have been removed.

00:06:51.159 --> 00:06:52.240
East of Jianguo Road

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:53.570
and north of Yuejin Road

00:06:53.800 --> 00:06:55.280
should be his hiding spot.

00:07:07.520 --> 00:07:08.360
Rest assured.

00:07:08.640 --> 00:07:10.200
I will obey orders

00:07:10.200 --> 00:07:10.840
and follow instructions this time,

00:07:10.840 --> 00:07:12.800
and guarantee to complete the task.

00:07:12.800 --> 00:07:13.440
I knew it.

00:07:13.520 --> 00:07:14.000
You are just

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:14.960
scolding me

00:07:15.040 --> 00:07:16.240
but caring for me deep down.

00:07:16.240 --> 00:07:16.970
Have a smoke.

00:07:17.320 --> 00:07:18.320
Remember to stand

00:07:18.400 --> 00:07:19.400
upwind next time.

00:07:20.600 --> 00:07:21.840
So you won't smell the corpses.

00:07:21.840 --> 00:07:23.000
But you can smell

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:24.560
how cowardly you are.

00:07:25.200 --> 00:07:26.000
Reporting to Captain Sun.

00:07:26.000 --> 00:07:26.800
I-I-I...

00:07:26.800 --> 00:07:28.480
I'm the new intern officer, Jia Peng.

00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:29.200
Starting today,

00:07:29.200 --> 00:07:30.560
I'll be learning from you.

00:07:30.560 --> 00:07:31.200
I promise

00:07:31.240 --> 00:07:32.200
to wait on you and prepare documents.

00:07:32.200 --> 00:07:33.640
I'll serve tea, pour water, and take notes.

00:07:33.640 --> 00:07:34.440
If you get bored,

00:07:34.440 --> 00:07:35.360
I can even play the clappers

00:07:35.360 --> 00:07:36.360
to cheer you up.

00:07:37.360 --> 00:07:38.000
Read this.

00:07:42.760 --> 00:07:43.840
What are you waiting for?

00:07:43.840 --> 00:07:44.640
Get in the car.

00:08:12.160 --> 00:08:13.320
We are police.

00:08:14.640 --> 00:08:15.900
Being a police officer

00:08:16.080 --> 00:08:18.610
means facing danger or even death at any time.

00:08:19.160 --> 00:08:20.760
We are all prepared for this.

00:08:21.240 --> 00:08:22.280
I made the plan.

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:24.560
I gave the orders.

00:08:25.560 --> 00:08:26.760
I sent Jia Peng there.

00:08:26.760 --> 00:08:28.020
He is a police officer.

00:08:28.040 --> 00:08:30.400
It's his duty to protect people's lives.

00:08:30.760 --> 00:08:32.000
Don't lecture me.

00:08:34.200 --> 00:08:35.530
What are you going to do?

00:08:35.880 --> 00:08:37.240
I'll go catch the killer.

00:08:37.240 --> 00:08:38.280
I'll shoot him.

00:08:38.919 --> 00:08:40.080
Can you calm down?

00:08:40.520 --> 00:08:42.720
Is this how a police captain should act?

00:08:44.640 --> 00:08:46.300
Jia Peng sacrificed himself.

00:08:46.360 --> 00:08:47.880
But the case must go on.

00:08:51.840 --> 00:08:53.280
The best way to honor him

00:08:54.440 --> 00:08:55.400
is to help him

00:08:56.560 --> 00:08:57.440
solve the case.

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:03.800
The killer tracked him to Lianshui,

00:09:03.800 --> 00:09:06.200
meaning he has ways to get Liu Jiang's info.

00:09:06.760 --> 00:09:08.320
And Liu Jiang's wife's phone

00:09:08.320 --> 00:09:09.800
happened to go missing that day.

00:09:09.800 --> 00:09:11.480
The killer used her phone

00:09:11.600 --> 00:09:13.200
to get Liu Jiang's location.

00:09:14.120 --> 00:09:16.120
Through the phone's last location,

00:09:16.440 --> 00:09:18.170
we deduced the killer's route.

00:09:18.640 --> 00:09:19.920
His last hiding spot

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:21.980
should be east of Jianguo Road

00:09:22.080 --> 00:09:23.480
and north of Yuejin Road.

00:09:45.280 --> 00:09:46.740
The killer's plan failed.

00:09:47.160 --> 00:09:48.840
He will definitely strike again.

00:09:48.840 --> 00:09:50.360
We must get ahead of him

00:09:51.080 --> 00:09:52.140
and find Liu Jiang.

00:09:55.200 --> 00:09:55.800
Xiaolin.

00:09:56.600 --> 00:09:57.880
Did the killer leave

00:09:57.880 --> 00:09:59.340
any evidence at the scene?

00:10:04.560 --> 00:10:06.480
I fired when the killer escaped.

00:10:07.040 --> 00:10:08.240
The bullet was found,

00:10:08.880 --> 00:10:10.840
but there was only a little blood on it,

00:10:10.840 --> 00:10:11.840
and it was contaminated.

00:10:11.840 --> 00:10:13.360
The DNA couldn't be identified.

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:14.280
I am certain

00:10:14.920 --> 00:10:17.180
that he was at least grazed by the bullet.

00:10:53.280 --> 00:10:53.760
Also,

00:10:55.560 --> 00:10:56.960
I found this at the scene.

00:10:58.600 --> 00:11:00.640
I've finished the initial registration,

00:11:00.640 --> 00:11:01.280
and I'm about to

00:11:01.280 --> 00:11:02.240
go to the evidence room

00:11:02.240 --> 00:11:02.960
to store it.

00:11:09.760 --> 00:11:10.480
Come here.

00:11:10.720 --> 00:11:11.800
These are the amulets

00:11:11.800 --> 00:11:13.530
your mentor's wife prayed for.

00:11:13.680 --> 00:11:14.960
Xiaoyan, Sun Xun, Guannan,

00:11:14.960 --> 00:11:15.560
one for each of you.

00:11:15.560 --> 00:11:16.200
Thank you. Thank you.

00:11:16.200 --> 00:11:16.930
Thanks, Mom.

00:11:38.280 --> 00:11:39.320
The hiding area

00:11:40.520 --> 00:11:42.450
matches his residential address.

00:11:43.480 --> 00:11:44.740
On the day of the crime,

00:11:44.960 --> 00:11:46.160
he had no alibi.

00:11:47.400 --> 00:11:48.800
Especially that amulet.

00:11:50.400 --> 00:11:51.480
Combined with

00:11:51.480 --> 00:11:52.880
our criminal profiling.

00:11:54.080 --> 00:11:56.680
Which one of these doesn't match Zhou Guannan?

00:11:57.200 --> 00:11:58.800
When Huguang went bankrupt,

00:11:59.440 --> 00:12:01.370
he was still in college out of town.

00:12:01.440 --> 00:12:02.480
About the master,

00:12:02.720 --> 00:12:04.560
I've always felt guilty towards him.

00:12:04.560 --> 00:12:06.490
That night in the relocation area,

00:12:06.880 --> 00:12:07.720
he performed

00:12:08.320 --> 00:12:10.050
a fire-breathing clown for us.

00:12:10.480 --> 00:12:11.360
I'm very sad.

00:12:12.520 --> 00:12:13.920
I thought I knew him well,

00:12:15.400 --> 00:12:17.330
but actually, I don't know anyone.

00:12:18.840 --> 00:12:20.370
There are 365 days in a year.

00:12:20.600 --> 00:12:22.060
There are 24 hours in a day.

00:12:23.160 --> 00:12:24.120
How could we know

00:12:24.160 --> 00:12:26.020
how he spent every single minute?

00:12:26.680 --> 00:12:27.320
Maybe

00:12:28.680 --> 00:12:30.610
he is no longer the Guannan we knew.

00:12:37.480 --> 00:12:38.040
Yan.

00:12:40.800 --> 00:12:42.130
What if it really is him?

00:12:48.640 --> 00:12:49.440
I don't know.

00:12:53.760 --> 00:12:55.290
I haven't thought about it.

00:12:59.440 --> 00:13:00.280
But I do know

00:13:02.600 --> 00:13:04.730
I will do what a police officer should.

00:14:27.560 --> 00:14:28.120
Suppose,

00:14:28.840 --> 00:14:30.960
every time the killer murders someone,

00:14:30.960 --> 00:14:32.020
he leaves flowers.

00:14:32.680 --> 00:14:35.340
But after he found out Liu Jiang faked his death,

00:14:35.440 --> 00:14:36.560
he moved this pot

00:14:36.560 --> 00:14:37.090
Hostess.

00:14:37.560 --> 00:14:38.490
of flowers away.

00:14:40.040 --> 00:14:40.840
Photo.

00:14:41.920 --> 00:14:42.600
Liu Jiang.

00:14:44.160 --> 00:14:45.220
Guan Jing's death.

00:14:56.840 --> 00:14:58.280
Guan Jing's death certificate

00:14:58.280 --> 00:15:00.410
was highly likely forged by Liu Jiang.

00:15:00.680 --> 00:15:01.320
Her death

00:15:01.520 --> 00:15:03.520
must be related to all these people.

00:15:04.160 --> 00:15:04.960
And the killer

00:15:05.320 --> 00:15:07.850
is very likely seeking revenge for Guan Jing.

00:15:08.120 --> 00:15:09.760
The cause of Guan Jing's death

00:15:09.760 --> 00:15:10.960
is perhaps the secret

00:15:11.440 --> 00:15:13.370
these people want to hide the most.

00:15:13.440 --> 00:15:14.600
If it's for revenge,

00:15:14.680 --> 00:15:16.000
why wait five years?

00:15:16.560 --> 00:15:18.160
Who exactly took the photos?

00:15:18.920 --> 00:15:19.600
The killer,

00:15:20.760 --> 00:15:22.320
or the killer's next target?

00:15:22.320 --> 00:15:24.440
Once we find the person who took the photos,

00:15:24.440 --> 00:15:25.160
everything

00:15:25.800 --> 00:15:26.800
will be answered.

00:15:32.120 --> 00:15:32.680
Look,

00:15:33.360 --> 00:15:34.490
how beautiful it is.

00:15:38.360 --> 00:15:39.280
Today,

00:15:40.280 --> 00:15:41.680
I have prepared a

00:15:41.840 --> 00:15:43.000
surprise for you.

00:15:43.760 --> 00:15:45.360
You will definitely like it.

00:15:46.240 --> 00:15:47.080
Because

00:15:47.760 --> 00:15:50.160
you are the student I personally selected,

00:15:50.680 --> 00:15:51.400
so

00:15:51.920 --> 00:15:53.160
I also personally had

00:15:53.280 --> 00:15:55.340
a set of clothes custom-made for you.

00:15:56.480 --> 00:15:57.560
Go try it on.

00:16:10.680 --> 00:16:11.600
So beautiful.

00:16:12.240 --> 00:16:13.240
Looking at you,

00:16:14.160 --> 00:16:15.620
I'm even a little tempted.

00:16:15.920 --> 00:16:17.520
I admire my own taste so much.

00:16:18.320 --> 00:16:19.440
You and this dress

00:16:20.040 --> 00:16:22.160
blend together perfectly.

00:16:25.080 --> 00:16:26.520
But I found a problem.

00:16:27.360 --> 00:16:28.620
You've gained weight.

00:16:29.360 --> 00:16:30.800
We have an exam coming up soon.

00:16:30.800 --> 00:16:32.600
So eat less these couple of days.

00:16:32.840 --> 00:16:34.400
It's all for your own good.

00:16:37.400 --> 00:16:38.280
I know

00:16:38.440 --> 00:16:39.970
your birthday is coming up,

00:16:40.000 --> 00:16:41.040
so I

00:16:41.400 --> 00:16:43.480
carefully picked out a

00:16:44.440 --> 00:16:45.700
birthday gift for you.

00:16:46.560 --> 00:16:48.280
To be a good actor,

00:16:49.120 --> 00:16:51.640
you must enrich your life experience.

00:16:52.680 --> 00:16:53.840
You need to interact with more people

00:16:53.840 --> 00:16:55.100
and observe them more.

00:16:56.560 --> 00:16:57.640
You also need to know how to

00:16:57.640 --> 00:16:58.720
package yourself

00:16:58.760 --> 00:17:00.020
and promote yourself.

00:17:00.600 --> 00:17:04.079
Always preserve your brightest image.

00:17:04.280 --> 00:17:05.720
This is the wisdom

00:17:05.720 --> 00:17:07.560
a good actor should have.

00:17:08.319 --> 00:17:09.160
Fast forward.

00:17:34.480 --> 00:17:35.560
After returning home,

00:17:35.560 --> 00:17:36.890
he never came out again.

00:17:37.960 --> 00:17:39.020
If that's the case,

00:17:39.560 --> 00:17:40.560
it can serve

00:17:41.000 --> 00:17:42.320
as part of the alibi.

00:17:42.720 --> 00:17:43.720
Not necessarily.

00:17:43.760 --> 00:17:44.890
You once told me that

00:17:45.720 --> 00:17:47.250
evidence is left by people.

00:17:48.120 --> 00:17:49.320
It can be fabricated,

00:17:49.880 --> 00:17:50.800
and it can be concealed.